  "body": "https://github.com/ethereum/tests/pull/934\r\n\r\ncheck if there are transaction tests for nonce: \r\n\r\n- [ ] maxAllowedNonce         must fail\r\n- [ ] maxAllowedNonce + 1  must fail\r\n- [ ] maxAllowedNonce - 1   must pass\r\n- [ ] pow(2,256)-1                 must fail \r\n- [ ] > pow(2,256)                 must fail\r\n- [ ] 00 before the nonce value  must fail\r\n empty rlp string  80 or 00 in transaction rlp  (one of this must fail)  it is 0x:bigint \r\n- [ ] \"0x:bigint 0x\"\r\n- [ ] \"0x:bigint 0x00\" \r\n\r\nthis can actually be a template for all transaction field values. \r\n(should think about it more see if we can invent more cases)\r\n",
