    "body": "The following tests are covered:\r\n- maxAllowedNonce: TransactionTests/ttNonce/TransactionWithHighNonce64\r\n- maxAllowedNonce + 1: TransactionTests/ttNonce/TransactionWithHighNonce64Plus1\r\n- maxAllowedNonce - 1: TransactionTests/ttNonce/TransactionWithHighNonce64Minus1\r\n- pow(2,256)-1: TransactionTests/ttNonce/TransactionWithHighNonce256\r\n- \\> pow(2,256): TransactionTests/ttNonce/TransactionWithNonceOverflow\r\n- 00 before the nonce value: TransactionTests/ttNonce/TransactionWithLeadingZerosNonce\r\n\r\nMissing tests:\r\n- \"0x:bigint 0x\": Passes\r\n- \"0x:bigint 0x00\": Fails with \"rlp: non-canonical integer\"\r\n\r\nI think the two state test cases implemented in #934 are very important for the coverage of the nonce.\r\n\r\nI will submit a PR for the two missing TransactionTests test cases.",
